<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Saul_Bellow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Novels and novellas">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Novels and novellas</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Dangling_Man" title="Dangling Man">Dangling Man</a></i> (1944)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Victim_(novel)" title="The Victim (novel)">The Victim</a></i> (1947)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Adventures_of_Augie_March" title="The Adventures of Augie March">The Adventures of Augie March</a></i> (1953)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Seize_the_Day_(novel)" title="Seize the Day (novel)">Seize the Day</a></i> (1956)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Henderson_the_Rain_King" title="Henderson the Rain King">Henderson the Rain King</a></i> (1959)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Herzog_(novel)" title="Herzog (novel)">Herzog</a></i> (1964)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Mr._Sammler%27s_Planet" title="Mr. Sammler's Planet">Mr. Sammler's Planet</a></i> (1970)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Humboldt%27s_Gift" title="Humboldt's Gift">Humboldt's Gift</a></i> (1975), won the 1976 <a href="/wiki/Pulitzer_Prize_for_Fiction" title="Pulitzer Prize for Fiction">Pulitzer Prize</a></li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Dean%27s_December" title="The Dean's December">The Dean's December</a></i> (1982)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/More_Die_of_Heartbreak" title="More Die of Heartbreak">More Die of Heartbreak</a></i> (1987)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/A_Theft" title="A Theft">A Theft</a></i> (1989)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Bellarosa_Connection" title="The Bellarosa Connection">The Bellarosa Connection</a></i> (1989)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Actual_(novel)" title="The Actual (novel)">The Actual</a></i> (1997)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Ravelstein" title="Ravelstein">Ravelstein</a></i> (2000)</li>
</ul>
