<li><a href="http://saulbellow.org/NavigationBar/titlepage.html" class="external text" title="http://saulbellow.org/NavigationBar/titlepage.html" rel="nofollow">Annotated Bibliography of Criticism</a> by the Saul Bellow Society</li>
<li><a href="http://www.hwwilson.com/Print/10bellowsa.html" class="external text" title="http://www.hwwilson.com/Print/10bellowsa.html" rel="nofollow">Bellow's 1955 autobiographical statement for reference book</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/17110" class="external text" title="http://www.nybooks.com/articles/17110" rel="nofollow">JM Coetzee on the early novels</a></li>
