<span style="font-size:110%;"><a href="/wiki/List_of_Nobel_laureates#Literature" title="List of Nobel laureates">Nobel Laureates</a> in <a href="/wiki/Nobel_Prize_in_Literature" title="Nobel Prize in Literature">Literature</a></span></th>
